d operating the plant without required pollution control equipment and construction permits in february  in respond to an epa ruling genon energy announced they would be shutting down the portland generating station in  reliant energy claims to have made efforts toward more environmentally safe practices through the use of renewable resources such as solar energy wind power landfill gas and coal refuse see alsoedit houston portal companies portal energy portal centerpoint energy deregulation of the texas electricity market electric reliability council of texas ercot california electricity crisis referencesedit  yahoo  rri energy inc company profile  contact us rri energy retrieved on january    a b mirant and rri energy complete merger pdf press release genon energy dec   archived from the original pdf on  retrieved apr     httpsfinanceyahoocomnewsnrggenoncompletemergercreatinghtmlpermanent dead link  nrg energy to buy genon for  billion  whats new at hlp  houston lighting  power february   retrieved on april    journal steven lipin staff reporter of the wall street  houston industries will buy noram energy for  billion wall street journal issn  retrieved    houston industries silent on merger report houston business journal november   retrieved on april    houston industries takes new name houston business journal february   retrieved on april    exelon bids for major texas power producer nrg houston chronicle october   retrieved on april   the plants were originally part of the former houston lighting  power the integrated utility that served the houston area until it was broken up into three separate companies as the state deregulated its power markets  fowler tom  houston power plants to be sold to nrg houston chronicle october   retrieved on april    new york times  reliant told of indictment  reliant indicted for manufacturing california energy crisis  nevada power plans to buy plant sources say las vegas reviewjournal p d march     political economy research 